1
00:00:04,120 --> 00:00:10,187
Krishna only wants love and affection.

2
00:00:10,671 --> 00:00:13,980
[Heart to Heart Connection]

3
00:00:14,700 --> 00:00:19,473
Whether it is from Chinese, 
American, Russian, Indian.

4
00:00:19,473 --> 00:00:23,908
This theme about heart ...

5
00:00:23,908 --> 00:00:29,018
Krishna consciousness 
is a heart to heart connection.

6
00:00:29,408 --> 00:00:38,910
So only the body is a Chinese body, 
a Thai body, American body,

7
00:00:38,910 --> 00:00:43,340
but there is not a Chinese soul, 
American soul, Thai soul, Indian soul ...

8
00:00:43,340 --> 00:00:46,481
Like we say, “For every action 
equal opposite reaction.”

9
00:00:46,481 --> 00:00:49,793
So there is some action in the past

10
00:00:49,793 --> 00:00:53,543
that necessitated 
that someone is born in China,

11
00:00:53,543 --> 00:00:56,752
someone’s born in Thailand, 
someone’s born in America,

12
00:00:56,752 --> 00:00:58,642
someone’s born in Russia.

13
00:00:58,642 --> 00:01:04,878
But the important thing to understand 
is the heart to heart connection.

14
00:01:05,582 --> 00:01:09,536
From the heart of Krishna 
to the heart of the devotee.

15
00:01:09,536 --> 00:01:17,297
And that transcends geography, 
politics,

16
00:01:17,297 --> 00:01:23,847
geopolitical, socio-economic 
circumstances.

